      <title>加拿大前总理哈珀有望出任艾伯塔省养老金主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/former-canadian-prime-minister-harper-eyed-as-alberta-pension-chairman</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿尔伯塔省政府已考虑聘请加拿大前总理斯蒂芬·哈珀 (Stephen Harper) 来监管其公共养老基金管理公司，由于上周该基金所有董事均被解雇，目前该基金已没有常设董事会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/former-canadian-prime-minister-harper-eyed-as-alberta-pension-chairman</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 17:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳的多元化发展有望吸引富裕的非洲人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/botswana-s-diversification-drive-seen-luring-wealthy-africans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，博茨瓦纳正努力实现经济多元化，从采矿业转向金融服务业，这将使其能够与毛里求斯竞争，成为非洲高净值个人和家庭的中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/botswana-s-diversification-drive-seen-luring-wealthy-africans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金 Ilex、Shiprock 也纷纷向新资金关闭大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/hedge-funds-ilex-shiprock-join-peers-closing-doors-to-new-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在大部分对冲基金行业现金大量流失的同时，一些公司却面临着资金充裕的问题，今年将是至少十年来最严重的问题之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/hedge-funds-ilex-shiprock-join-peers-closing-doors-to-new-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
